Input: A = "aabc"
Output: "a#bb"
Step-by-step:

a â†’ first unique: 'a'

a â†’ no unique: '#'

b â†’ first unique: 'b'

c â†’ first unique: 'b' (as 'b' is still unique)

â± Time & Space Complexity
Time: O(n), where n is the length of string A.

Space: O(1), as frequency array is fixed size (26).

